    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250080/extras/6d5001288460e9d1017fd3137b73e994.avif?t=1769530635\" width=1560 height=297 /></span> <br>在这款像素艺术冒险游戏中，你将扮演Psycasso®——一位在开放世界城市中挣扎求生的画廊艺术家。白昼你需从事日常工作赚取金钱并提升技能，完美融入社会；入夜后则需伺机从“行走的肉袋”身上采集“红色颜料”，以此创作原创2D艺术作品。将画作售予画廊获取巨额利润！运用潜行技巧与独特陷阱躲避日益严密的警方追捕，凭借独创艺术作品发家致富。在这款前所未有的争议性独立游戏中，购置房产、升级装备、布置家具、收集武器，探索繁华都市并体验丰富迷你游戏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250080/extras/ff6552b739ca8ae3ec574b3c65bfb7b1.avif?t=1769530635\" width=1560 height=486 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250080/extras/ba6aaabec759109d122a2c6656997658.avif?t=1769530635\" width=1560 height=297 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◘ 2D绘画系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◘ 画廊任务与拍卖会</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◘ 开放世界城市环境</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◘ 技能升级与装备强化</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◘ 日夜交替系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◘ 32位像素艺术画风</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◘ 可购置房产与家具升级 <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250080/extras/14752504555b69d6275eb708d30f5990.avif?t=1769530635\" width=1560 height=486 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250080/extras/d3f7fc888a047d90392d4b51b907f29e.avif?t=1769530635\" width=1560 height=297 /></span><br>⦾ 钓鱼系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦾ 潜行机制</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦾ 街机游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦾ 新增武器与道具</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦾ 剧情驱动任务</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦾ 新增建筑地点</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦾ 新增地图区域</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦾ 升级光照系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦾ 升级视觉特效</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦾ 音频优化</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦾ 手机功能扩展</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦾ 玩家社区请求内容</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦾ 更多血腥效果！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦾ 更多语言翻译</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250080/extras/c01752807d9ceebab41bc286b7a1a04b.avif?t=1769530635\" width=1560 height=297 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作说明：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >键盘/鼠标：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >移动 - 上/下/左/右</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动作1 - F</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动作2 - E</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动作3 - G</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动作4 - R</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速槽位 - W/A/S/D</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >步行模式 - Shift/Ctrl</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >缩放 - Alt</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主菜单 - Esc</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瞄准 - Y / 右键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >攻击 - J / 左键点击</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏手柄：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Playstation)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >移动 - 左摇杆</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动作1 - X键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动作2 - 方块键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动作3 - 圆圈键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动作4 - 三角键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快捷槽 - 方向键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >步行模式 - R1/L1</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >缩放 - L3</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主菜单 - Start键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瞄准 - L2键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >攻击 - R2</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏手柄：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Xbox)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >移动 - 左摇杆</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动作1 - A键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动作2 - X键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动作3 - B键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动作4 - Y键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快捷槽 - 方向键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >步行模式 - RB/LB键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >缩放 - 左摇杆（推）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主菜单 - Start键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瞄准 - 左肩键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >攻击 - 右肩键</p>",
